/////////////////////////////////---------------- THA 4 ------ HOW INTERNET WORKS & REST APIs AND INTRO TO NODE.JS ---------------------////////////////////


___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
__________________________________________________________| PROTOCOLS (Rules) Of Data Package |____________________________________________________________________________

Sets the Rules of Data Package

>>> TCP / IP
Transport Data

>>> HTTP / HTTPS
Web Access

>>> RTP
Live Video 
Streaming 
VOIP Calls (VOIP means Voice over Internet Protocol) 


__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
________________________________________________________| API (APPLICATION PROGRAMMING INTERFACE) |_______________________________________________________________________


Set of Programming Codes that enables Data Transmission between one Software Product and Another.


///////////////////// ------------------------------------------ | HOW API WORKS | -----------------------------------------------------////////////////////// 


Web App in Browser      <- Request / Response ->    [ Internet ]   <------>    { API }     <------->      Web Server   --------   Database


___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
________________________________________________________________| TYPES OF API |___________________________________________________________________________________________

>>> PRIVATE  = localhost

>>> PARTNER  = partner api use for company 

>>> PUBLIC   = anyone use public api like netflix

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
__________________________________________________________________| REST API | ____________________________________________________________________________________________

REST : Representatable State Transfer

> Simple and Standard
> Scalable and Stateless
> High Perfomance, can be cached


Create     =>   POST
Read       =>   GET
Update     =>   PUT
Delete     =>   DELETE 

_____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
___________________________________________________________________| REQUEST |_______________________________________________________________________________
SENDING A REQUEST 

> Header (Some Keys)
> Param / Body (Request Data)
> Operations 
> End Point 

______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
___________________________________________________________________| RESPONSE |________________________________________________________________________________
RECEIVING  RESPONSE 

> Header
> JSON

